Load Olympic CSV Data

Source: R/load_data.R
load_olympic_csv_data.Rd

Given a Sport ID and Match ID, load a pre-parsed CSV of data from that event

Usage

load_olympic_csv_data(sportID, matchID)

Source

NBC API

Arguments

sportID

Sport ID

matchID

Match ID

Value

A data.frame

Author

Billy Fryer

Examples

# \donttest{
load_olympic_csv_data(sportID = 113, matchID = 746587)
